<div style="padding:5px;font-size:small">
<p><b>Whakaahua o te wā: <i>Kei Taupiri, 1846</i>: ko te pā o Te Wherowhero mā</b></p>
<p><br>
</p>
<figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Taupiri.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Ko te whakaahua o te wā"><img alt="Ko te whakaahua o te wā" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Taupiri.jpg/330px-Taupiri.jpg" decoding="async" width="330" height="232" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Taupiri.jpg/500px-Taupiri.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/05/Taupiri.jpg 2x" data-file-width="540" data-file-height="380"></a><figcaption>Ko te whakaahua o te wā</figcaption></figure>
<p><br>
</p>
</div></div>
</td>
<td style="padding:4px;font-size:1px"> 
</td>
<td width="50%" valign="top">
<div style="margin-bottom:1.25em;border:1px solid #8898BF; background:transparent;padding:0">
<div style="height:8px;margin:0;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid #8898BF;background: #C8D8FF;font-size:1px"></div>
<div style="padding:5px;font-size:small">
<p><b>Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau</b></p>
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:M45_filip.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau"><img alt="Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/M45_filip.jpg/250px-M45_filip.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="154" class="mw-file-element" data-file-width="1200" data-file-height="738"></a><figcaption>Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau</figcaption></figure>He kāhui whetū e whitu a <a href="/wiki/Matariki" title="Matariki">Matariki</a>, e mōhiotia nei ko <i>Pleiades</i>. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou. 
<p>He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.
</p>
</div></div>
<div style="margin-bottom:1.25em;border:1px solid #8898BF; background:transparent;padding:0">
<div style="height:8px;margin:0;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid #8898BF;background: #C8D8FF;font-size:1px"></div>
<div style="padding:5px;font-size:small">
<p><b>Kua mōhio rānei koe...</b></p>
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa"><img alt="Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg/120px-MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg" decoding="async" width="120" height="176" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg/250px-MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg 1.5x" data-file-width="712" data-file-height="1042"></a><figcaption>Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa</figcaption></figure>
<p>Ko <a href="/wiki/Meri_Te_Tai_Mangak%C4%81hia" title="Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia">Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia</a> te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko <a href="/wiki/H%C4%81miora_Mangak%C4%81hia" title="Hāmiora Mangakāhia">Hāmiora Mangakāhia</a>, he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga. 
</p><p>Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.
</p>
</div></div>
<div style="margin-bottom:1.25em;border:1px solid #8898BF; background:transparent;padding:0">
<div style="height:8px;margin:0;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid #8898BF;background: #C8D8FF;font-size:1px"></div>
<div style="padding:5px;font-size:small">
<p><b>Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai</b></p>
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Nmahutawoman.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta"><img alt="He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Nmahutawoman.jpg/40px-Nmahutawoman.jpg" decoding="async" width="40" height="70" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Nmahutawoman.jpg/60px-Nmahutawoman.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Nmahutawoman.jpg/120px-Nmahutawoman.jpg 2x" data-file-width="448" data-file-height="783"></a><figcaption>He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta</figcaption></figure>Tēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia" title="Wikipedia">Wikipedia</a> Māori hei <a href="/wiki/M%C4%81t%C4%81punenga" title="Mātāpunenga">mātāpunenga</a> utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. Tirohia ēnei tuhipānui papai:
<p><a href="/wiki/Aoraki" title="Aoraki">Aoraki</a> • <a href="/wiki/Aotearoa_Tuatahi" title="Aotearoa Tuatahi">Aotearoa Tuatahi</a> • <a href="/wiki/Te_Atairangikaahu" title="Te Atairangikaahu">Te Atairangikaahu</a> • <a href="/wiki/Hoani_Nahe" title="Hoani Nahe">Hoani Nahe</a> • <a href="/wiki/Lili%27uokalani" title="Lili'uokalani">Lili'uokalani</a> • <a href="/wiki/Marae" title="Marae">Marae</a> • <a href="/wiki/Te_Rangi_H%C4%ABroa" title="Te Rangi Hīroa">Te Rangi Hīroa</a> • <a href="/wiki/Reo_M%C4%81ori" title="Reo Māori">Reo Māori</a> • <a href="/wiki/Takuu" title="Takuu">Takuu</a> • <a href="/wiki/Te_Aroha" title="Te Aroha">Te Aroha</a> • <a href="/wiki/Tongariro" title="Tongariro">Tongariro</a> • <a href="/wiki/Wiremu_Maihi_Te_Rangik%C4%81heke" title="Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke">Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke</a>
</p>
</div></div>

    Whakaahua o te wā: Kei Taupiri, 1846: ko te pā o Te Wherowhero mā



    		  

    Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau

    He kāhui whetū e whitu a Matariki, e mōhiotia nei ko Pleiades. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou.

    He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.

    Kua mōhio rānei koe...

    Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko Hāmiora Mangakāhia, he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga.

    Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.

    Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai

    Tēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te Wikipedia Māori hei mātāpunenga utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. Tirohia ēnei tuhipānui papai:

    Aoraki • Aotearoa Tuatahi • Te Atairangikaahu • Hoani Nahe • Lili'uokalani • Marae • Te Rangi Hīroa • Reo Māori • Takuu • Te Aroha • Tongariro • Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke

Nō Wikipedia Māori

Haeremai ki Wikipedia, te mātāpunenga wātea mā te katoa e whakatika

E 8,011 ngā tuhipānui reo Māori

 Rapu, Tikanga rapu

Wāhanga · Rārangi-ā-pū · Tuhipānui papai · Rārangi

 
Mahi ngātahi ki te hapori

Hapori · Tikanga · Mahi whakatika · Pātai mai · Māngai (Embassy)

Whakaahua o te wā: Kei Taupiri, 1846: ko te pā o Te Wherowhero mā



  

Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau

He kāhui whetū e whitu a Matariki, e mōhiotia nei ko Pleiades. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou.

He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.

Kua mōhio rānei koe...

Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko Hāmiora Mangakāhia, he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga.

Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.

Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai

Tēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te Wikipedia Māori hei mātāpunenga utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. Tirohia ēnei tuhipānui papai:

Aoraki • Aotearoa Tuatahi • Te Atairangikaahu • Hoani Nahe • Lili'uokalani • Marae • Te Rangi Hīroa • Reo Māori • Takuu • Te Aroha • Tongariro • Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke

images.alt: Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau
images.desc:
Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau
Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tauHe kāhui whetū e whitu a Matariki, e mōhiotia nei ko Pleiades. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou. 
He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.

images.alt: Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa
images.desc:
Kua mōhio rānei koe...
Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa
Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko Hāmiora Mangakāhia, he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga. 
Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.

images.alt: He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta
images.desc:
Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai
He wahine rangatira o Ngāti MahutaTēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te Wikipedia Māori hei mātāpunenga utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. Tirohia ēnei tuhipānui papai:
Aoraki • Aotearoa Tuatahi • Te Atairangikaahu • Hoani Nahe • Lili'uokalani • Marae • Te Rangi Hīroa • Reo Māori • Takuu • Te Aroha • Tongariro • Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke

**Whakaahua o te wā:_Kei Taupiri, 1846_ : ko te pā o Te Wherowhero mā**
  

[![Ko te whakaahua o te wā](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Taupiri.jpg/330px-Taupiri.jpg)](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Taupiri.jpg "Ko te whakaahua o te wā")Ko te whakaahua o te wā
  

|  **Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau** [![Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/M45_filip.jpg/250px-M45_filip.jpg)](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:M45_filip.jpg "Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau")Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tauHe kāhui whetū e whitu a [Matariki](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matariki "Matariki"), e mōhiotia nei ko _Pleiades_. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou. He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.  **Kua mōhio rānei koe...** [![Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, \(1868-1920\) nō Te Rarawa](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg/120px-MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg)](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg "Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, \(1868-1920\) nō Te Rarawa")Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa Ko [Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meri_Te_Tai_Mangak%C4%81hia "Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia") te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko [Hāmiora Mangakāhia](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C4%81miora_Mangak%C4%81hia "Hāmiora Mangakāhia"), he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga.  Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.  **Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai** [![He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Nmahutawoman.jpg/40px-Nmahutawoman.jpg)](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Nmahutawoman.jpg "He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta")He wahine rangatira o Ngāti MahutaTēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te [Wikipedia](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia "Wikipedia") Māori hei [mātāpunenga](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C4%81t%C4%81punenga "Mātāpunenga") utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. |  **Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau** ![Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau⟨100⟩](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:M45_filip.jpg "Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tau")Ko Matariki, te whetū o te tauHe kāhui whetū e whitu a Matariki⟨101⟩, e mōhiotia nei ko _Pleiades_. I ia hōtoke, ko te putanga mai o Matariki hei whakaatu mai kua pau te tau tawhito, kua tīmata he tau hou. Mai rā anō, ko te putanga mai o Matariki he wā whakanui, he wā whakatikatika hoki mō te tau hou. He wā whakareri a Matariki i te whenua. I waenganui o te hōtoke i te wā o Matariki, e āhua moe kē ana te whenua. Ka whakatōngia he hua whenua hei koha ki ngā atua o te whenua. Ka tata te kōanga te tae mai, kāhore atu he wā i te wā o Matariki hei whakatakoto kaupapa mō te whenua, mō ngā mahi whenua hoki o te kōanga āianei. He wā pai hoki hei ako i ngā āhuatanga o te whenua me te ngahere.  **Kua mōhio rānei koe...** ![Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, \(1868-1920\) nō Te Rarawa⟨102⟩](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:MeriMangakahia1890s.jpg "Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, \(1868-1920\) nō Te Rarawa")Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia, (1868-1920) nō Te Rarawa Ko Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia⟨103⟩ te wahine tuatahi i tū ki te kōrero ki te Pāremata Māori o Te Kotahitanga? I whānau mai ia i te 22 o Mei 1868 i tētahi wāhi e tata ana ki Panguru i te moana o Te Hokianga. Ko tana tāne ko Hāmiora Mangakāhia⟨104⟩, he rangatira o Hauraki i tohungia i 1892 hei Pirimia mō te Pāremata Māori, arā mō te Kotahitanga.  Nō te 18 o Mei i te tau 1893 i tū te hui a te Pāremata o te Kotahitanga i Heretaunga; ka puta te motini a Meri Te Tai Mangakāhia kia whai wāhi ngā wāhine ki te pōtitanga. Ka tū a Meri ki te tautoko ki tana mōtini i roto i te Pāremata – ko ia tonu te wahine tuatahi i kōrero ki taua huinga.  **Nau mai, haere mai, tomo mai** ![He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta⟨105⟩](https://mi.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Nmahutawoman.jpg "He wahine rangatira o Ngāti Mahuta")He wahine rangatira o Ngāti MahutaTēnā koe! Haere mai! Kua hangaia te Wikipedia⟨106⟩ Māori hei mātāpunenga⟨107⟩ utukore, hei mātāpunenga māhorahora. Ko te nako o tēnei mātāpunenga he rerekē: ka taea e ia tangata, e ia tangata, te tuhituhi, te whakatika rānei, i ngā tuhipānui o te paetukutuku nei. Ko te mahi mā tātou, he waihanga tuhipānui hou, he whakatika, he whakaroa i aua tuhipānui. Tirohia ēnei tuhipānui papai: Aoraki⟨108⟩ • Aotearoa Tuatahi⟨109⟩ • Te Atairangikaahu⟨110⟩ • Hoani Nahe⟨111⟩ • Lili'uokalani⟨112⟩ • Marae⟨67⟩ • Te Rangi Hīroa⟨113⟩ • Reo Māori⟨15⟩ • Takuu⟨114⟩ • Te Aroha⟨115⟩ • Tongariro⟨116⟩ • Wiremu Maihi Te Rangikāheke⟨117⟩
